{"tid":2212770,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"陳同佳不如開個YouTube channel 做youtuber喇","createTime":"2020-09-22T05:03:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-24T08:25:19.000Z","uid":309192,"like":36,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"3019c00fdc5fa39f4e4515e6d92dd51baefcd084","tid":2212770,"uid":309192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T05:03:25.000Z","msg":"本身佢個故事已經好戲劇性<br />\n仲可以攪到香港滿城風雨<br />\n同時更為香港台灣支那關係急劇升溫<br />\n分分鐘WWIII 既起因都可能因為佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲痴線既係<br />\n番到黎咁耐 台灣都打開哂大門<br />\n都仲一拖再拖仲未去接受審訊<br />\n<br />\n依家仲係有狗保護既豪宅入面住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n工又唔做番<br />\n野又唔使做<br />\n又有人養<br />\n<br />\n不如佢拍下：<br />\n殺人犯的日常生活<br />\n五個殺人要注意既地方<br />\n殺人犯出沒！首次到CWB Donki購買感想<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />為佢傳奇一生留下記錄"},{"pid":"97b3c12ec63769e4e4e7a7c3f2da4158906904f9","tid":2212770,"uid":122134,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T05:04:52.000Z","msg":"講下個度會所係點<br />\n畢竟無咩人見識過"},{"pid":"dde0a47711f2a8891521ad69d96b1bde8682e638","tid":2212770,"uid":127929,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T05:05:01.000Z","msg":"殺人犯的日與夜"},{"pid":"ad375a003506452836e168d4da617bbbedb373de","tid":2212770,"uid":357803,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T06:19:51.000Z","msg":"佢都出唔到門口啦<br />\n<br />\n一出門口就係過街老鼠"},{"pid":"1e106836817c61c01ae4b716f026b8cd88701641","tid":2212770,"uid":10903,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ad375a0035